divs: Sighting DetailsSaw my first fastwalker yesterday around 6:30 sun going down to my back, looking up saw what I first thought might be a silver bird, very high up, spurting forward at different speeds, then when in line with half moon in northern sky flashed and gone in a second at tremendous speed.
